window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>I never wanted to need him, but when my boyfriend cheats on me, I decide to get a little revenge...by sleeping with his father. </b></p> <p>Tyler. <i>Mr. Phillips</i>. The silver fox that fills my fantasies and has been off limits…until now. Our one night together turns into more than we could have ever imagined. But when real life explodes into our torrid romance, can we handle what it brings?</p> <p>Hearts are broken, lives are ruined. If we can survive the world pulling us apart, we just might have a chance at a happily ever after. Buckle up daddy, I’m about to be your angel.</p> <p>Screw you Justin, your dad does it better.</p> <p><i>Daddy's Angel </i>contains dark elements which some listeners may find triggering. All characters in this story are over eighteen and all sexual interactions are fully consensual.</p>"; 
